OL,3,CChief executive of Head of the Public
OL,4,CService announced
OL,6,FGuernsey Post's boss will become the
OL,7,Fisland's next Chief Executive and Head
OL,8,Fof the Public Service in early 2025.
OL,10,FThe Policy and Resources Committee
OL,11,Fselected Guernsey-born Boley Smillie
OL,12,Fafter the current Chief Executive,
OL,13,FMark de Garis, announced he would
OL,14,Fleave the position in August.
OL,16,FBoley was educated at La Mare de
OL,17,FCarteret School before beginning his
OL,18,Fcareer at Guernsey Post in 1991 where
OL,19,Fhe became CEO in 2010.
