OL,3,CChief executive of Head of the Public
OL,4,CService announced
OL,6,FHe has also been the Non-Executive
OL,7,FChairman of Guernsey Mind for the last
OL,8,Ffive years.
OL,10,FSpeaking about his new role, Smillie
OL,11,Fsaid: "I am honoured to be given the
OL,12,Fopportunity to lead the public
OL,13,Fservice, and I can't wait to get
OL,14,Fstarted next year.
