OL,3,CChief executive of Head of the Public
OL,4,CService announced
OL,6,F"Throughout my time at Guernsey Post,
OL,7,FI've been proud of the positive
OL,8,Fdifference that our team makes to
OL,9,Fislanders and businesses across the
OL,10,FBailiwick and I'm looking forward to
OL,11,Fcontinuing this work through the
OL,12,Fpublic service.
OL,14,F"I will focus my energies on
OL,15,Fsupporting colleagues and elected
OL,16,Fmembers to deliver the best outcomes
OL,17,Ffor our community."
