OL,3,CChief executive of Head of the Public
OL,4,CService announced
OL,6,FDeputy Lyndon Trott, President of the
OL,7,FPolicy and Resources Committee, said:
OL,8,F"We are very much looking forward to
OL,9,Fworking with Boley.
OL,11,F"He impressed the panel throughout the
OL,12,Finterview process, combining a strong
OL,13,Funderstanding of the challenges and
OL,14,Fopportunities facing Guernsey with a
OL,15,Ffresh perspective on the public
OL,16,Fservice.
OL,18,F"I am very grateful to Mark de Garis,
OL,19,Fthe current Head of the Public
OL,20,FService, for agreeing to provide a
OL,21,Fstructured handover."
